data.meta_description: Visit Now or Order Online | Discover a taste sensation at our Red Robin restaurant in Woodburn, Oregon. Treat yourself to our famous burgers, bottomless fries, and a welcoming atmosphere.
data.text:
About Us

You never know where you'll be when the craving for a thicker, juicier burger will strike. Maybe you're shopping, maybe you're touring the Oregon Electric Railway Museum or maybe you're hanging out at Centennial Park. Wherever you happen to be, there's only one place to help you satisfy that hunger, and that's your Woodburn Red Robin. Located on Sprague Lane, you'll find over 25 Gourmet Burgers to choose from; including our new Lava Queso, the Monster, The Southern Charm, our Cheesy Bacon Fondue and our fan fave Whiskey River® BBQ. Any of these burgers pair perfectly with our iconic Bottomless Steak Fries®.
